msgstr "« %s » dupliquée."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:674
msgid "Duplicate pattern"
msgstr "Dupliquer la composition"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:675
msgid "Duplicate"
msgstr "Dupliquer"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:727
msgid "Pattern renamed"
msgstr "Composition renommée"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:733
msgid "An error occurred while renaming the pattern."
msgstr "Une erreur est apparue lors du renommage de la composition."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:750 wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1153
msgid "Rename"
msgstr "Renommer"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:782 wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1197
msgid "Save"
msgstr "Enregistrer"

#. translators: %s: the name the user has given to the pattern.
#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:893
msgid "Unsynced pattern created: %s"
msgstr "Composition non synchronisée créée : %s"

#. translators: %s: the name the user has given to the pattern.
#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:897
msgid "Synced pattern created: %s"
msgstr "Composition synchronisée créée : %s"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:916
msgid "Create pattern"
msgstr "Créer une composition"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1016 wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1023
msgid "Detach"
msgstr "Détacher"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1025
msgid "Detach pattern?"
msgstr "Détacher de la composition ?"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1027
msgid ""
"The blocks will be separated from the original pattern and will be fully "
"editable. Future changes to the pattern will not apply here."
msgstr ""
"Les blocs seront séparés de la composition originale et seront complètement "
"modifiables. Les évolutions futures de la composition ne s’appliqueront pas "
"ici."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1029
msgid ""
"Blocks will no longer be associated with this pattern and will be fully "
"editable."
msgstr ""
"Les blocs ne seront plus associés avec cette composition et seront "
"complètement modifiables."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1035
msgid "Manage patterns"
msgstr "Gérer les compositions"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1100
msgid "Please enter a new name for this category."
msgstr "Merci de saisir un nouveau nom pour cette catégorie."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1109
msgid "This category already exists. Please use a different name."
msgstr "Cette catégorie existe déjà. Merci d’utiliser un nom différent."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1131
msgid "Pattern category renamed."
msgstr "La catégorie de composition a été renommée."

#. translators: %s: new name/label for the block
#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1231
msgid "Block name changed to: \"%s\"."
msgstr "Le nom du bloc a été modifié pour : « %s »."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1242 wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1409
msgid "Enable overrides"
msgstr "Autoriser les remplacements"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1258
msgid ""
"Overrides are changes you make to a block within a synced pattern instance. "
"Use overrides to customize a synced pattern instance to suit its new "
"context. Name this block to specify an override."
msgstr ""
"Les remplacements sont des modifications que vous effectuez au bloc d’une "
"instance de composition synchronisée. Utilisez les remplacements pour "
"personnaliser une instance de composition synchronisée. Donnez un nom à ce "
"bloc pour spécifier qu’il s’agit d’un remplacement."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1267
msgid ""
"For example, if you are creating a recipe pattern, you use \"Recipe Title\", "
"\"Recipe Description\", etc."
msgstr ""
"Par exemple, si vous créer une composition de recette, vous utilisez « Titre "
"de la recette », « Description de la recette », etc."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1291
msgid "Enable"
msgstr "Activer"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1306 wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1409
msgid "Disable overrides"
msgstr "Neutraliser les remplacements"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1319
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to disable overrides? Disabling overrides will revert "
"all applied overrides for this block throughout instances of this pattern."
msgstr ""
"Êtes-vous certaine de vouloir neutraliser les remplacements ? La "
"neutralisation des remplacements annulera tous les remplacements appliqués à "
"ce bloc dans toutes les instances de cette composition."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1338
msgid "Disable"
msgstr "Neutraliser"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1381
msgid ""
"Overrides currently don't support image links. Remove the link first before "
"enabling overrides."
msgstr ""
"Les remplacements ne supportent pas les liens d’images. Retirer le lien "
"préalablement à l’activation des remplacements."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1383
msgid "Allow changes to this block throughout instances of this pattern."
msgstr ""
"Autoriser les modifications à ce bloc pour toutes les instances de cette "
"composition."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/patterns.js:1492
msgid "Reset"
msgstr "Réinitialiser"
